<A NAME = "9"></A>Copyright
INNOVATOR'S DIGEST via NewsNet
January 9, 1996

FIBROUS COMPOSITES IN STRUCTURAL DESIGN [960109]

This (Federal Aviation Agency) document contains the
proceedings of a conference on fibrous composites in
structural design (Nov. 4-7, 1991, Lake Tahoe, NV).  It
contains reprints of over 30 presentations on the
subject, including, for example: developmental problems
and their solutions; space shuttle problems, fixes, and
applications; process and control systems for
composites manufacturing; fabric preforms; static and
dynamic testing; fatigue testing; composite fuselage
panels and fabrication; structural applications;
assembly delaminations; stress analysis and failure;
finite element analysis; design; various applications;
and much more.

(Order this INNOVATOR'S DIGEST reviewed report from
InfoTeam Inc., P.O. Box 15640, Plantation, FL
33318-5640; Phone (954)/or(305) 473-9560, Fax
(954)/or(305) 473-0544: Report No. D601DB; Sep. 1992,
483 pp.  Price: $499.00, prepaid.)




