NORTHWESTERN'S TECH PROGRAM

Northwestern University is $47 million toward its goal of raising
$90 million for its academic technology program. The campaign
will provide funds for the complete reconstruction of the Chicago
University's Technological Institute building, and endowment
support for exceptional faculty, graduate student fellowships,
the library,laboratories and other needs.




