BIO-TECH TRANSFER.

        The Biotechnology Information Institute has just published
the Federal Bio-Technology Transfer Directory. This 678-page book
describes all federal biomedical and basic biotechnology
inventions and technology transfer agreements. The book provides
data about licenses and partnering agreements. Call 301/424-0257.



