BellSouth Mobility, 15 Century Blvd., 2 Lakeview Place, Suite 200,

BellSouth Mobility, 15 Century Blvd., 2 Lakeview Place, Suite 200, Nashville,
TN 37214, 615/871-2000, has donated $3000 worth of cellular equipment and
airtime to the "Parkwatch" security program sponsored by Friends of Warner
Parks, a volunteer organization committed to supporting the Warner Parks
system.  The donation includes 3 transportable phones plus airtime.  Parkwatch
volunteers will place a "highly visible" sign on their private vehicles as they
patrol the parks, looking for suspicious activities, which they will then
report to the authorities.



