Centel Cellular recently honored its 100,000th customer, Jay Haviland of

Centel Cellular recently honored its 100,000th customer, Jay Haviland of
Harrisburg, Pa., by awarding him a free cellular phone and a trip for 2 to Walt
Disney World.  The company also offered 100 free minutes of airtime to
customers who signed up during the week-long 100,000th customer celebration.
The company provides service in 44 markets nationwide and has interests in 14
others.  (Centel Cellular Co., O'Hare Plaza, 8725 Higgins Rd., Chicago, IL
60631, 800/323-2174 or 312/399-2500.)



