Technophone Corp. (NEW ADDRESS:  1801 Penn St., Suite 3, Melbourne, FL

Technophone Corp. (NEW ADDRESS:  1801 Penn St., Suite 3, Melbourne, FL 32901,
407/952-2100) is expected to introduce a new transportable, the model TC905A,
