Would you believe that NovAtel showed more than 1000 new products at the

Would you believe that NovAtel showed more than 1000 new products at the show?
Neither did we until NovAtel Carcom VP-general manager Ira Tabankin explained
how they do it.  NovAtel manages this incredible feat of manufacturing by
producing a line of different-on-the-outside handset styles but using the same
innards.  "We're showing about 75 different [handsets] in this booth,"
Tabankin said. The OEM buyer can select the style and the color for deliveries.
